    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "fair enough. so if the system is fundamentally built around the interests of a few big powers, does that mean the whole idea of \"international law\" or \"collective security\" is just an illusion? or is there a way historians see the UN actually working for everyone else?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
